data.description: This charming log home is almost 1,300 sqft and is located in the cute small town of Dorris, CA - just minutes from the Oregon border. The house has 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, a full basement for storage. There is an AMAZING 1,200 sqft building that could be utilized for a number of uses: think additional living space, workout area, party room, workshop, you name it! Also on the property is a metal 3 car garage with additional storage area. The yard is fenced with a nice yard and landscaping - there is even a plum tree!
